  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees.",
    "Cut the red bell peppers into 1-inch pieces and thread onto skewers.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together fish sauce, lime juice, honey, garlic, and ginger.",
    "Brush the mixture onto the peppers.",
    "Drizzle coconut oil over the peppers.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper.",
    "Bake for 20 minutes or until crispy.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy."
